                <note rend="inline" type="source">721.23/734: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Ambassador in Peru</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Dearing</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1933-01-18T13:00:00-05:00"
                            >January 18, 1933—1 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>14. Your telegram No. 21, January 15, 11 a.m. Please endeavor to obtain from the
                    Brazilian Minister a copy of his note to Peru of January 13, and cable the
                    Department the text thereof. Also text of Peruvian reply.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Stimson</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
